{"tid":328930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[健身健心] 鍛鍊身體幾問求教","createTime":"2017-07-20T03:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T19:02:43.000Z","uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09c1b385124d8ff3be86e153487cf9dd14110417","tid":328930,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"繼我先前問過巴打點減磅後，經過一輪食物控制同做運動。 <br />\n成功極速由157磅跌落150磅（唔該晒巴打先），我178CM高，睇數字就好標準喇。 <br />\n<br />\n咁我上網睇計翻個脂肪比例，用以下equation計<br />\n體脂 ％ = 1.2 x BMI + 0.23 x 年齡 - 5.4 - 10.8x性別(男=1)<br />\n計出嚟係15.8%，under30男性標準係14-18%，咁應該都好標準啦。 <br />\n但係d肉感覺都係鬆鬆地，肚腩修咗但都仲係搣到舊肉。 <br />\n<br />\n運動就keep住隔2-3日跑步，跑完做吓push up。 <br />\n無跑步就玩dumb bell，格日就練下腹，唔算intense但keep住會train下。 <br />\n<br />\n想問下而家呢個身型點樣可以進一步修線條？係咪一定要出去gym room做會好啲？<br />\n另外係咪應該繼續減脂呢？<br />\n而家上腹係見到少少嘅，但肚個位感覺好難練，請教有咩方法可以操下？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6dbef70568cfeb2a9dafba97fcab1af413cc3e","tid":328930,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:47:05.000Z","msg":"有無健身jj呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba457325a54921a9d1bd0b52b257e56de45972e2","tid":328930,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"有無巴打啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae402001c67592c6179b45a30b7ce04d854b756d","tid":328930,"uid":111148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"有無健身巴打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63fe777984492b0f541eff98f00bd3620b5d765","tid":328930,"uid":72346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T16:52:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd